data.description: This beautiful 3 bed 2 bath home has so much character, it’s conveniently located near the Toledo Zoo and the Maumee River. It is in a quiet neighborhood that dead-ends into the park, walk to Glass City Dog Park, and Walbridge Park. Fresh new paint throughout the entire home, new flooring throughout, with tons of space and storage. Glass block windows in basement and can easily be a rec room. Eat-in kitchen with Frigidaire Elite stainless steel appliances & over 20 ft. counter space! Bedrooms are huge with closet space to match. There is a full bath with standing shower on the first floor.
